{"word":"Jedaiah","slug":"jedaiah","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Jedaiah</b> <a href=\"#/H3042\">H3042</a><br/><a href=\"#/H3048\">H3048</a> <br/> 1. Descendant of Simeon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=4&verse=37'>1Ch 4:37</a><br/> 2. A returned exile<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=3&verse=10'>Neh 3:10</a><br/> 3. A priest of the captivity<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=9&verse=10'>1Ch 9:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=24&verse=7'>1Ch 24:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=2&verse=36'>Ezr 2:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=7&verse=39'>Neh 7:39</a><br/> 4. A priest who dwelt at Jerusalem after the return of the captivity<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=11&verse=10'>Neh 11:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=6'>Neh 12:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=19'>Neh 12:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=6&verse=10'>Zec 6:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=6&verse=14'>Zec 6:14</a><br/> 5. Another priest, who returned from Babylon with Nehemiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=7'>Neh 12:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=21'>Neh 12:21</a>"}]}